title: 4YE's Big Movie Binge: Home Again (2017)
body:
Credit: Black Bicycle Entertainment

Home Again, Reece Witherspoon’s most recent romantic comedy, and the film that was supposed to mark her return to the genre, falls flat in so many different ways. It’s a shame that the filmmakers didn’t recognize the problems the film had while in production. They might have been able to fix this train wreck.

What makes things worse is Home Againhad a terrific…

title: 4YE's Better Late Than Never: Masters Of Sex (Season One)
body:
4YE’s Better Late Than Never: Masters Of Sex (Season One)

Credit: Showtime

William Masters and Virginia Johnson were at the cutting edge of scientific exploration in the mid-1950s with the introduction of their study on the bodily responses to sexual stimulation both alone and with a partner. It was a study that revolutionized people’s understandings of the human body and sex. In an era where sex and radicalization were taboo, Masters and Johnson bucked…

summary: 50% of all Good Omens fanfiction is written by Michael Sheen. David Tennant writes 45% of it but has his wife post it because he...
body: 50% of all Good Omens fanfiction is written by Michael Sheen. David Tennant writes 45% of it but has his wife post it because he can’t figure out how, 3% is written by Neil Gaiman (who may or may not be possessed by the ghost of Terry Pratchett), and the remaining 2% is written by the fandom.

summary: Okay a few months ago I had this weird galaxy brain thing where I realized at certain angles David Tennant looks like a...
body: Okay a few months ago I had this weird galaxy brain thing where I realized at certain angles David Tennant looks like a scraggly, skinny, deranged Hugh Jackman, and now it’s happening again and I’m just gonna say it. Certain pictures of Michael Sheen from the late 1990s remind me of George Blagden.
